==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfurl
<hw>Un*furl"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>furl</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loose from a furled
state; to unfold; to expand; to open or spread; <as>as, to
<ex>unfurl</ex> sails; to <ex>unfurl</ex> a flag.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

